*xen-3.0.0_pre20051007 (08 Oct 2005)

  08 Oct 2005; Chris Bainbridge <chrb@gentoo.org> files/xend-init,
  files/xendomains-conf, files/xendomains-init,
  -xen-3.0.0_pre20050929.ebuild, +xen-3.0.0_pre20051007.ebuild:
